name: Rumah Makan Kenanga Jawa Timur
address: Sanggalangit, Gerokgak, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81155, Indonesia
review 1:
Nice place to transit in the north of Bali.
There are several bathrooms with hot water for only Rp. 7000.  if you want privater you can also rent a room.
review 2: Thanks for service but you have to maintenance your toilet. When somebody flush in your side room their waste will appear at your closed.
review 3: This place has a great scenery
review 4: The food is good. The place is huge. I like the ricefields on the backyard. Their people are nice and polite too.
review 5: Love this place.  Beautiful view with delicious food.  Clean and green.
